  "instructions": [
    "In a large pan, heat olive oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add chicken and sauté until cooked through, approximately 5 minutes on each side.",
    "Remove chicken from the pan and set aside. Add bell peppers to the pan and stir-fry for about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Return chicken to the pan with bell peppers, add orange segments and a squeeze of lemon juice.",
    "Mix in grated ginger and chopped cilantro until well combined.",
    "Season with salt to taste and serve immediately."
